# HIIT Timer (`projects/hiit-timer/`)

Configurable interval timer. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS.

## Defaults

- Work: 20 seconds
- Rest: 30 seconds
- Rounds: 8 (user-configurable, saved in `localStorage` keys `hiit-work`, `hiit-rest`, `hiit-rounds`, `hiit-sound`)

## Style

- Match site palette; use `--work` and `--rest` accent colors for phases
- Left-aligned layout like other projects
